0acquisitions%2C%20and%20still%20now%20at%20his%20new%20ad%20company%2C%20S4%20Capital%2C%20is%20an%20archetypal%20%26quot%3BDavos%20Man%2C%26quot%3B%20often%20seen%20on%20stage%20and%20TV%20offering%20commentary%20about%20macroeconomic%20issues.%20Read%20has%20kept%20a%20lower%20profile%20and%20has%20sought%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwpp-ceo-mark-read-turnaround-challenges-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esimplify%20WPP's%20many%20agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20more%20uniform%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESorrell%20did%20%26quot%3Bempire%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20%26quot%3BRead%20has%20been%20an%20empire%20dismantler%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20independent%20media%20analyst%20Alex%20DeGroote%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Read%20WPP%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dc4779e3afd37465834c173%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERead%20became%20WPP%20CEO%20in%202018.%3Cp%3EWPP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20industry%20analysts%20and%20insiders%20say%20this%20is%20to%20Read's%20credit.%20According%20to%20DeGroote's%20calculations%2C%20Read%20retired%20around%20300%20different%20agency%20brands%2C%20closed%20more%20than%20800%20offices%2C%20and%20realized%20around%20%245.1%20billion%20for%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkantar-ceo-talks-about-wpp-spinoff-bain-capital-ownership-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrom%20disposals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20WPP%20reduced%20its%20net%20debt%20to%20around%20%242.3%20billion%20as%20of%20December%2031%20last%20year%2C%20down%20from%20about%20%243.4%20billion%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Read%20era%20of%20restructuring%20and%20layoffs%20has%20hit%20morale%20within%20the%20rank%20and%20file%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mood%20that%20was%20further%20soured%20among%20some%20WPP%20employees%20when%20