%20astonishing%20average%20of%2011%2C872%20milimetres%20of%20rain%20each%20year.%20The%20region%20has%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20monsoon%20seasons%2C%20from%20June%20to%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20of%20this%20region%20is%20not%20solely%20defined%20by%20its%20statistics.%20Visitors%20to%20Mawsynram%20often%20find%20themselves%20entranced%20by%20the%20symphony%20of%20rain%2C%20each%20drop%20singing%20a%20lullaby%20to%20the%20vibrant%20greens%20that%20carpet%20the%20earth.%20It%20is%20a%20place%20where%20the%20rain%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20merely%20fall%3B%20it%20sings%2C%20dances%2C%20and%20transforms%20the%20landscape%20into%20a%20paradise%20abundant%20with%20biodiversity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20wondered%20why%20northeast%20India%20receives%20such%20heavy%20rainfall%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Professor%20Upma%20Chaturvedi%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Geography%2C%20Avadh%20Girls%E2%80%99%20Degree%20College%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20to%20learn%20the%20science%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Findian-monsoon-2-1749465569.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20maps%20show%20both%20actual%20dates%20and%20early%20onset%20of%20Southwest%20monsoon%20this%20year.%20Image%20source%3A%20IMD%2C%20Wikipedia%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Findian-monsoon-2-1749465569.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Findian-monsoon-2-1749465569-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Findian-monsoon-2-1749465569-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Findian-monsoon-2-1749465569-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Findian-monsoon-2-1749465569-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-446417%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20maps%20show%20both%20actual%20dates%20and%20the%20early%20onset%20of%20the%20Southwest%20monsoon%20this%20year.%20Image%20source%3A%20IMD%2C%20Wikipedia%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20important%20factors%20to%20note%20are%20the%20physical%20and%20geographical%20features%20that%20influence%20rainfall%20there.%20%E2%80%9CTwo%20key%20elements%20are%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20relief%20and%20latitude.%20The%20first%20factor%20is%20the%20area%E2%80%99s%20unique%20topography%2C%20and%20then%20the%20southwest%20monsoon%2C%20which%20is%20followed%20by%20orographic%20rainfall%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%E2%80%9CThe%20eastern%20Himalayan%20range%20and%20the%20hills%20in%20Meghalaya%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Assam%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20Southwest%20monsoon.%20The%20bend%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20range%20towards%20the%20northeast%2C%20known%20as%20the%20syntaxial%20bend%2C%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20it%20like%20this%3A%20the%20region%20acts%20like%20a%20giant%20natural%20funnel.%20During%20summer%2C%20the%20land%20heats%20up%20and%20creates%20a%20low-pressure%20area.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20summer%2C%20winds%20from%20t