20fruit%20tree%20saplings%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20being%20mangoes%2C%20without%20charging%20a%20single%20penny.%20In%202024%20alone%2C%20he%20received%20around%2011%20lakh%20seeds%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20From%20these%2C%20with%20care%20and%20patience%2C%20he%20nurtured%20around%2080%2C000%20grafted%20saplings%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%20of%20the%20mango%20seeds%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20mango%20season%2C%20his%20home%20becomes%20a%20warehouse%20for%20mango%20seeds.%20But%20his%20family%20supports%20him%20through%20it%20all.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%2C%20Anju%2C%20bears%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20madness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20chuckles.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20she%20has%20never%20complained.%20She%20knows%20how%20important%20this%20work%20is%20to%20me%20and%20supports%20me%20whenever%20I%20need%20her.%E2%80%9D%20His%20daughters%2C%20too%2C%20play%20a%20fundamental%20role%20in%20expanding%20the%20initiative%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424613%2Fshalini-robert-social-work-love-healing-education-sponsorship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelping%20with%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20packaging%2C%20and%20spreading%20the%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20support%20keeps%20growing.%20Schools%20across%20Kolkata%2C%20such%20as%20La%20Martiniere%2C%20St%20Xavier%E2%80%99s%2C%20and%20Birla%20High%2C%20have%20run%20their%20%3Cem%3Egutli%20%3C%2Fem%3Edrives%2C%20educating%20students%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20environment.%20The%20entrepreneur%20expresses%20proudly%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20same%20people%20who%20laughed%20and%20were%20unsure%20in%20the%20beginning%20are%20now%20collecting%20seeds%20for%20me.%20This%20is%20what%20makes%20me%20believe%20that%20I%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20driving%20the%20initiative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigu