9s%20this%20urgency%20and%20opportunity%20that%20drives%20BCML%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20help%20make%20this%20bio-revolution%20happen%E2%80%A6%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20excites%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20future%20of%20plastics%20via%20Balrampur%20Bioyug%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Avantika%20envisions%20a%20future%20where%20BCML%20harnesses%20the%20full%20potential%20of%20PLA%20once%20the%20plant%20starts%20functioning%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20five%20years%2C%20I%20want%20to%20maximise%20the%20potential%20of%20PLA.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20can%20do%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20the%20ambition%20is%20clear%2C%20it%20will%20require%20collective%20movement%20across%20industry%20and%20government.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20broader%20goal%20includes%20exploring%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F124274%2Fbioplastic-prawn-shells-angelina-arora-sydney-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiomaterials%20and%20green%20chemicals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20long-term%20value%20addition.%20For%20Avantika%2C%20sustainability%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20strategy%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20default.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20we%20do%20is%20inherently%20sustainable%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20rooted%20in%20agriculture.%20From%20reducing%20water%20usage%20to%20cutting%20chemical%20inputs%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20doing%20more%20with%20less%20%E2%80%94%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20good%20for%20both%20the%20planet%20and%20the%20business.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCML%20is%20already%20collaborating%20across%20sectors%2C%20testing%20seven%20to%20eight%20different%20PLA%20applications%20and%20working%20closely%20with%20industries%20to%20ensure%20adoption.%20%E2%80%9CNet%20Zero%202070%20won%E2%80%99t%20happen%20on%20its%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20group%20effort.%20And%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20our%20part.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20fully%20operational%2C%20the%20Bioyug%20plant%20will%20produce%2080%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20PLA%20annually%20%E2%80%94%20potentially%20replacing%20over%20millions%20of%20plastic%20bottles%20or%20packaging%20units%20each%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Stefan%2C%20sharing%20a%20glimpse%20of%20a%20powerful%20revolution%20in%20combating%20plastic%20waste%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWant%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20bio-based%20future%3F%20Visit%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chini.com%2F%5C%22%3E%20www.chini.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20follow%20BCML%20or%20Balrampur%20Bioyug%20on%20LinkedIn%20to%20stay%20updated%20about%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20progress%20and%20manufacturing.%20Because%20the%20future%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20grow%20in%20labs.%20Sometimes%2C%20it%20grows%20in%20cane%20fields%20and%20changes%20everything.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%20Castelino%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Balrampur%20Chini%20Mills%20Limited.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749099600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-03T140040.298-1749033760.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D444154%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Balrampur%20Bioyug%2C%20born%20from%20a%20granddaughter%E2%80%99s%20vision%20and%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20legacy%2C%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20PLA.%20The%20brand%2C%20launched%20by%20Balrampur%20Chini%20Mills%2C%20aims%20to%20turn%20sugar%20derived%20from%20sugarcane%20into%20bio-plastics%20%E2%80%94%20and%20can%20rewrite%20what%20sustainability%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20circular%20economy%20can%20look%20like%20when%20rooted%20in%20Indian%20soil%20and%20purpose.%22%2C%22author%22%